data.description: Welcome to 3601 Oak Cliffs Ave. This Charming 3 Bedroom 2 Bathroom home is turn-key and is nestled in a friendly neighborhood! This home boasts vaulted ceilings within an open, yet split- concept layout, maximizing space and functionality. The Kitchen features Sparkling Granite Countertops and an Island that overlooks the Causal Dining Area and Welcoming Living Room. You find that the backyard is low maintenance and fully walled for your privacy. This lot is oversized and offers Side Parking to accommodate all your toys! With its newer construction and affordable price point, this home offers an ideal opportunity to step into homeownership with ease and style!
